title: Aaron Rodgers, NFL ratings, Dalvin Cook, Carson Wentz
itunes:title: Aaron Rodgers, NFL ratings, Dalvin Cook, Carson Wentz
description:
Colin explains why he feels people don't like Aaron Rodgers, why NFL ratings will be down this season, why he likes Dalvin Cook but understands why he can't get paid, and why he is defending Carson Wentz. Guests include Jarrett Bell, Gerald McCoy, Bucky Brooks, and Howard Beck.
